- Fixes for events' reproducibility:
  o G4GammaConversion.cc: changed usage of RandFlat::shootBit() to
    RandBit::shootBit().
  o G4VIeEnergyLoss.cc, G4VIhEnergyLoss.cc, G4PAIxSectionTest.cc:
    changed RandGauss to G4RandGauss.

